@node %mopen "File - Open..."
@toc "Menu commands"
@autorefoff
Datei - ôffnen...                                                     Thing
@line 1 75 0 0 7
@autorefon

Selected objects are, where possible, opened.

Files - The appropriate installed application, if any, is started.

Programs/accessories -  The program/accessory is executed. If the program
  is already active Thing asks if a second copy should be started.
  Accessories are 'awoken' using a AC_OPEN or VA_START message.

Folders and drives - A new directory window is opened to display the
  contents.
@endnode

